{"tid":1298950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要置頂] 「社會信用系統」殺到埋黎，你唔需要再返大陸","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:40:46.000Z","uid":259166,"like":485,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"bd80af242e037678725ae681bf94e996b8f59c5b","tid":1298950,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"因為你已經企係大陸了！<br />\n<br />\n「社會信用系統」殺到，你評級係D級的話，死梗。<br />\n到時等同於活在一個監獄外的一個集體監獄！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2525251037525019&amp;id=972393926144079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2525251037525019%26id%3D972393926144079&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=3ebe3901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2525251037525019&amp;id=972393926144079</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文例子:<br />\n<br />\n中國「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬今年5月傳出被評為「D級」，除了被限制不得購買大眾運輸工具票券以外，徐曉冬也不能進入酒店和高爾夫球場、不准裝修、新建、擴建房屋，甚至連旅遊渡假也被禁止。<br />\n<br />\n到時實係全民造星，道德倫亡！悲哀。"},{"pid":"55ad3668ef7a77f2f7a476abd1ea977e61810437","tid":1298950,"uid":259166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:11:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我冇嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"bd3c6b1175fd4a99ee723278272191ba10070efb","tid":1298950,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我冇嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"5398960c91d7f04a6259944e0e4937a544d2dfaf","tid":1298950,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我冇嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"cfe6f51dfb7a9fe144c569ac7152952d9ef49c98","tid":1298950,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我冇嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"d2d31b790f4989cfda8dbe3ac112c81390b8155b","tid":1298950,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2